*LoPEC *************************
*Low Power Erlang-based Cluster* 
*Adding echo to wave file*******
********************************

--How to compile-- 
run the Makefile  


--How to run-- 
run the program by typing 
> ./echo inputfile.wav 
the output you will receive is a new file 
called out.wav  

---This is just made for research purpose--- 

This application was ment to be ported to OpenCL 
But we just did not have the time to do that in the scope
of this project.  

